Server:

1.- Open a command shell.
2.- go to the folder where the server jar (optserver.jar) was unzipped, using the cd command
3.- execute the following command:
java -jar optserver.jar -p <port-number> -k <key>

Client:

1.- Open a command shell.
2.- go to the folder where the client jar (optclient.jar) was unzipped, using the cd command
3.- execute the following command:
java -jar optclient.jar -p <port-number> -t <IP/hostname> -k <key> -s <message>

Notes:

To test both applications, the server must be running first
